---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Eyebrow from '../components/Eyebrow.astro';
import Hl from '../components/Hl.astro';
import Btn from '../components/Btn.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="About — AWJ"
  description="Andy Whyte. Founder/CEO, best-selling author, dad, human. Outcome-oriented, results-driven. MEDDIC superfan."
>
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="site-shell about-hero__inner">
      <div class="about-hero__copy">
        <Eyebrow>Who is this?</Eyebrow>
        <h1 class="about-hero__title awj-display">
          Andy Whyte. <Hl>Founder/CEO</Hl>, best-selling author, dad, human.
        </h1>
        <p class="about-hero__lead">Outcome-oriented, results-driven. MEDDIC superfan.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-hero__photo">
        <img src="/assets/images/andy_headshot_cutout.png" alt="Andy Whyte" loading="eager" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="manifesto content-shell">
    <div class="prose">
      <h2>Why this exists.</h2>
      <p>AWJ — the Andy Whyte Journal — is a personal intellectual operating system, expressed publicly. It's closer to a Munger notebook than a creator brand. The product is the thinking, not the personality.</p>

      <h2>Three pillars.</h2>
      <p><strong>Sales — authority.</strong> MEDDICC, deal inspection, sales as a thinking discipline.</p>
      <p><strong>Founder — operator.</strong> Bootstrap SaaS, trade-offs under uncertainty, no theatre.</p>
      <p><strong>Human — truth.</strong> Controlled lessons from failure. The quality of your thinking determines the quality of your life.</p>

      <h2>What this isn't.</h2>
      <p>Not hustle culture. Not build-in-public noise. Not performative vulnerability. Not generic corporate polish. Not safe.</p>

      <hr />

      <p>If that resonates, the journal arrives Fridays.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="manifesto__cta">
      <Btn href="/subscribe/" tone="dark">Subscribe to the journal</Btn>
      <Btn href="/journal/" tone="ghost">Read the archive</Btn>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero { padding: var(--sp-9) 0 var(--sp-7); border-bottom: var(--border-hard); }
  .about-hero__inner {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--sp-7);
    align-items: center;
  }
  @media (min-width: 900px) {
    .about-hero__inner { grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr; }
  }
  .about-hero__title {
    font-size: clamp(40px, 6.5vw, 96px);
    margin: var(--sp-3) 0 var(--sp-5);
    line-height: 0.95;
  }
  .about-hero__lead {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--fs-body-lg);
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--fg-2);
  }
  .about-hero__photo {
    background: var(--awj-yellow);
    background-image: url('/assets/textures/paper_yellow.png');
    background-size: cover;
    border: var(--border-hard);
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .about-hero__photo img {
    width: 90%;
    height: auto;
    filter: grayscale(1) contrast(1.05);
  }
  .manifesto { padding: var(--sp-8) var(--gutter) var(--sp-9); }
  .manifesto__cta {
    margin-top: var(--sp-7);
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--sp-3);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
</style>
